4. FILES YOU'LL CREATE
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Each file below will be created inside "functions/src/".
Create them in the order listed (Phase 1 first).

  📁 interfaces/               ← TypeScript interfaces
     ├── blogPost.ts           BlogPost interface
     ├── category.ts           Category interface
     └── report.ts             Report interface

  📁 CloudFunctions/           ← request handlers (the entry points)
     ├── cfCreatePost.ts       POST /blogPosts
     ├── cfGetPosts.ts         GET /blogPosts (with filters + pagination)
     ├── cfGetPost.ts          GET /blogPosts/<id> + triggers first-view
     ├── cfUpdatePost.ts       PUT /blogPost/<id>
     ├── cfDeletePost.ts       DELETE /blogPost/<id>
     ├── cfUpvote.ts           callable — upvote once
     ├── cfDownvote.ts         callable — downvote once
     ├── cfRevokeVote.ts       callable — revoke vote
     ├── cfAuthOnSignup.ts     fires when user signs up
     ├── cfRtdbOnFirstView.ts  fires on first read receipt
     ├── cfRtdbOnNewPost.ts    fires when post is created (init views/votes)
     ├── cfRtdbOnVote.ts       fires when vote changes
     ├── cfStorageOnImageUpload.ts  fires on image upload (resize)
     ├── cfPubsubDailyReport.ts     fires on schedule (daily report)
     └── cfGetReports.ts       GET /reports

  📁 DataAccess/Read/          ← reading from the database
     ├── getBlogPosts.ts       returns paginated + filtered posts
     ├── getBlogPost.ts        returns single post by id
     ├── getVote.ts            returns user's vote on a post
     └── getReports.ts         returns reports by date

  📁 DataAccess/Write/         ← writing to the database
     ├── setBlogPost.ts        creates a new post
     ├── setVote.ts            sets or removes a vote
     ├── setView.ts            marks a read receipt (first view tracking)
     └── setReport.ts          saves a report

  📄 index.ts                  ← wire everything together (already exists, edit it)

